ness~ to put us all together like this, all from different camps, and letting us shine. It's nice.","actor":900205},{"side":2,"bgName":"star_level_bg_121","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Well, if my Commander wishes it, I suppose I can muster up some motivation.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900204},{"bgName":"star_level_bg_121","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":2,"dir":1,"say":"Directives received. Switching functionalities.","actor":900203},{"bgName":"star_level_bg_121","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":3,"dir":1,"say":"Now... I don't actually know where to begin...","actor":900206},{"side":2,"bgName":"star_level_bg_121","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Anywhere's good, right~ Let's try this: the first song, \"c≈ìur.\" Ready? One, two, three...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900205},{"side":2,"bgName":"star_level_bg_121","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"And so, with a little hope and a lot of unease, the newly formed group, Polaris, practiced their hearts out...","blackBg":true,"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}}]}